data.title: Kelly Clarkson
data.meta_description: Kelly Clarkson is an American singer, songwriter, author, and television personality.
data.text:
Kelly Clarkson is an American singer, songwriter, author, and television personality.

History[edit]

During Simon Cowell audition for American Idol, a picture was seen.[1]

Krusty entertained at a party at Kelly Clarkson's house. The wall of her house had many pictures of Clarkson on.[2]

Appearances[edit]

Episode – "The King of Nice" (picture)

Special – The Simpsons Judge American Idol (picture)
